modules.description: Implements a vantage-point tree for efficient nearest-neighbor searches over a list of points. Provides operations to construct the tree, find the nearest neighbor to a given point, and convert the tree back to a list. Works directly with the point type defined in the P submodule, supporting use cases like spatial queries in geometric or high-dimensional data.

Implements a vantage-point tree for efficient nearest-neighbor searches over lists of points. Provides operations to build the tree from a list, find the nearest neighbor to a given point, and convert the tree back to a list. Works directly with the point type defined in the P submodule, enabling spatial queries in geometric or high-dimensional data.
